CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...13. The General Tire company booth, represented by Bill Carter, had an impressive display...Harris Photos"
